{
"#name"
:
{
"teeshot"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"运行命令并缓存输出,显示头尾样本"
,
"en"
:
"Run commands and cache output, show head/tail samples"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x teeshot <cmd>"
,
"x teeshot --cache ls"
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"把长命令的输出落到 cache,显示元数据 + 前 N / 后 M 行抽样,让 agent 或 shell 开发者不必重跑命令也能判断是否要细看。\n默认缓存到 ~/.x-cmd.root/cache/teeshot/<day>/<id>,其中 <day> 来自 `x epoch day`,为未来按天 TTL 清理服务提供基础;同一天同一命令命中同一缓存;支持 stdin 模式、--head/--tail 自定义抽样、--no-cache 跳过写入,以及 --cache 子命令管理快照。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Capture long-running command output to cache, display metadata + first N / last M lines as a sample, so agents or shell developers can decide whether to dig deeper without re-running the command. Caches to ~/.x-cmd.root/cache/teeshot/<day>/<id>, where <day> comes from `x epoch day` and lays the foundation for a future day-bucketed TTL cleanup service; same cmd on the same day hits the same cache; supports stdin mode, --head/--tail custom sample sizes, --no-cache to skip writes, and --cache subcommand for snapshot management.\n"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot ls /etc"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 跑命令,缓存输出,显示前 10/后 10 行 + 元数据"
,
"en"
:
"Example: run a command, cache output, show first 10/last 10 lines + metadata"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --head 10 --tail 5 ls -la /usr/bin"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 自定义抽样大小,只看前 10/后 5 行"
,
"en"
:
"Example: custom sample size, view only first 10/last 5 lines"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --no-cache uname -a"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 跑命令但不写缓存,只显示头尾样本"
,
"en"
:
"Example: run command but skip cache write, only show head/tail sample"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --head 20 --tail 10 x mac sysctl"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 长输出抽样,head/tail 用 TEESHOT fence + 行号范围包好,直接喂给 LLM"
,
"en"
:
"Example: sample a long output; head/tail are wrapped in TEESHOT fences with line ranges, ready to feed an LLM"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"dmesg | x teeshot"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 管道模式,把 stdin 当成捕获的输出,缓存并抽样显示"
,
"en"
:
"Example: pipe mode, capture stdin as output, cache and show sample"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --cache ls"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 列出所有缓存的快照(id / 退出码 / 行数 / mtime / cmd)"
,
"en"
:
"Example: list all cached snapshots (id / exit / lines / mtime / cmd)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --cache cat a1b2c3d4e5f60718"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看某快照的完整输出(从 --cache ls 拿 id)"
,
"en"
:
"Example: view full output of a snapshot (id from --cache ls)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --cache rm a1b2c3d4e5f60718"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 删除某个快照"
,
"en"
:
"Example: remove a snapshot"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --cache rm --all"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 删全部(交互确认 y/N)"
,
"en"
:
"Example: remove all (interactive confirm y/N)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --cache info a1b2c3d4e5f60718"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看某个快照的元数据(退出码、cwd、host、捕获模式)"
,
"en"
:
"Example: view metadata of a snapshot (exit, cwd, host, capture mode)"
}
]
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"agent 工作流: 跑了一个很长的命令(像 x mac sysctl 默认 1846 行),先 `x teeshot <cmd>` 看头尾 + 元数据,决定要不要 `x teeshot --cache cat <id>` 拿完整输出或调整 --head/--tail。避免 agent 反复重跑副作用命令。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Agent workflow: when running a verbose command (e.g. x mac sysctl default 1846 lines), use `x teeshot <cmd>` first to see head/tail + metadata, then decide whether to `x teeshot --cache cat <id>` for the full output or adjust --head/--tail. Avoids re-running side-effect commands.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"缓存 ID 规则: sha256(\"<cmd>|$HOSTNAME\" + 可选 stdin 内容哈希) 取前 16 字符 hex。同一命令在**同一天**同台机器上重跑会命中同一缓存,跨机器或跨天自动分离 —— 这是未来按天 TTL 清理服务的基础。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Cache ID rule: sha256(\"<cmd>|$HOSTNAME\" + optional stdin content hash), first 16 hex chars. Same command on the same host on the same day hits the same cache; different hosts or different days are auto-separated — this is the foundation for a future day-based TTL cleanup service.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"--no-cache 用于\"只想看这一次抽样,不想留垃圾缓存\"的场景,例如调试期的探索性命令。生产复现命令建议保留缓存,后续可以重复回看。\n"
,
"en"
:
"--no-cache is for \"I just want a one-shot sample, don't leave garbage\" cases (e.g. exploratory debugging). Reproducible production commands should keep the cache for later re-inspection.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"缓存目录在 ~/.x-cmd.root/cache/teeshot/,想清空时也可用 `x cleanup cache`(慎用,会清掉所有 x-cmd 缓存)或 `rm -rf ~/.x-cmd.root/cache/teeshot`。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Cache dir lives at ~/.x-cmd.root/cache/teeshot/. To wipe, use `x cleanup cache` (careful: clears all x-cmd caches) or `rm -rf ~/.x-cmd.root/cache/teeshot`.\n"
}
,
{
"cn"
:
"输出对 AI 友好: 默认抽前 10 / 后 10 行,head 与 tail 之间被省略的部分用 `<!-- TEESHOT:OMITTED -->` 标出,各段用 `<!-- TEESHOT:HEAD range=\"1-10\" -->` / `<!-- /TEESHOT:HEAD -->`(以及 FULL/OMITTED/TAIL)fence 包起来,HEAD/TAIL 还带上各自在原文的行号区间,LLM 能把它当结构边界而不是正文。fence 是 inert 的 shell 注释,可直接拼进 prompt;`--head`/`--tail` 可调抽样大小,`--no-cache` 只看不写。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Output is AI-friendly by construction: by default it samples the first 10 / last 10 lines, the omitted middle is marked with `<!-- TEESHOT:OMITTED -->`, and each section is wrapped in `<!-- TEESHOT:HEAD range=\"1-10\" -->` / `<!-- /TEESHOT:HEAD -->` (and FULL/OMITTED/TAIL) fences — HEAD/TAIL carry their line range in the original so an LLM treats them as structural delimiters rather than content. The fences are inert shell-style comments, safe to splice straight into a prompt; `--head`/`--tail` adjust the sample size and `--no-cache` shows without writing.\n"
}
]
,
"--cache"
:
{
"#subcmd"
:
true
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"管理 teeshot 缓存的快照(列出/查看/删除)"
,
"en"
:
"Manage teeshot cached snapshots (list/view/remove)"
}
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --cache ls"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 列出所有缓存的快照"
,
"en"
:
"Example: list all cached snapshots"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --cache cat <id>"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看某快照的完整输出"
,
"en"
:
"Example: view full output of a snapshot"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --cache rm <id>"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 删除某个或多个快照(可一次给多个 id)"
,
"en"
:
"Example: remove one or more snapshots (multiple ids at once)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --cache rm --all"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 删全部(交互确认 y/N)"
,
"en"
:
"Example: remove all (interactive confirm y/N)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x teeshot --cache info <id>"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看某快照的元数据,不打印内容"
,
"en"
:
"Example: view metadata of a snapshot, without printing content"
}
]
,
"ls"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"列出所有缓存的快照(id、退出码、行数、mtime、cmd)"
,
"en"
:
"List all cached snapshots (id, exit, lines, mtime, cmd)"
}
}
,
"cat"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"查看某个快照的完整输出"
,
"en"
:
"View full output of a snapshot"
}
}
,
"rm"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"删除快照(支持单个 id 或 --all 全部)"
,
"en"
:
"Remove snapshots (single id or --all)"
}
}
,
"info"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"查看某个快照的元数据(不打印内容)"
,
"en"
:
"View metadata of a snapshot (without printing content)"
}
}
}
}

